NELSON--Kenneth Warwick. Kenneth Warwick Nelson, 91, October 15, 1922 - July 29, 2014, formerly of Emerson Hill Staten Island, New York 10304. Beloved husband for 70 years of Carey Boone Nelson. Loving father of their six children: Caren Nelson Schubart, Kenneth Nelson II, Kimberley Nelson, Keith Nelson, Kyle Nelson Galante and Craig Nelson. Cherished grandfather of 17 grandchildren and eight great-grandchildren. Graduate of Massachusetts Institute of Technology with a Bachelor of Science Degree in Business, Engineering & Administration and Harvard Business School (U.S. Navy Officer's Program). Patents: Two-color injection molding of thermoplastic polymers. USA Patents #